    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Refers to the culture of Albania, either the modern nation in the western part of the Balkan peninsula, or the ancient province of Albania on the Caspian Sea.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
